item.description: Contributors for 8th Sem Thanks to them for making CSIT community a better place ! .ghContributors{ display:flex; flex-flow: wrap; align-content: flex-start } .ghContributors div{ width: 50% ; display: inline-flex; margin-bottom: 5px; } .ghContributors div label{ padding-left: 4px ; } .ghContributors div span{ font-size: x-small; padding-left: 4px ; } @csitauthority 1 commits And a very special thanks to @matcornic for his work on Hugo Theme Learn, a hugo port inspired by Grav Learn Theme.
